==People==
* Charles Blackstone (born 1977), fiction writer
* Elliott Blackstone (1924â2006), former police sergeant and LGBT advocate
* Gay Blackstone (born 1952), widow of Harry Blackstone, Jr.
* Harriet Blackstone (1864â1939), American painter
